snippet.title: MegaWorld Builder - Deisgn Your Dream House
snippet.description:
Explore the step-by-step process of creating a Project of your dream building in the MegaWorld! 

Open MegaWorld Builder: https://builder.megaworld.io/
Official MegaWorld website: https://www.megaworld.io/
Ask the community: https://create.megaworld.io/

From designing your project in the powerful MegaWorld Builder to deploying it on a land plot parcel within the MegaWorld Strategy mode, you'll discover how to craft a one-of-a-kind living and working space for your Avatar.
